::Proto/Grimmler::

Proto, Grimmler, and the interior defences stop firing as Twister and Dracona 
leave. Proto looks down at his wrist comp. "If these Preds don't get more 
serious, they'll never bring down the shields."

Grimmler grins. "Probably. I'm going to go on patrol, see ya later."

Proto nods, walking into the base as Grimmler flies off.
